  <brief_title>Safety and Preliminary Efficacy of Activated Recombinant Human Factor VII in Acute Intracerebral Haemorrhage</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomised, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Multicentre, Dose-Escalation Study to Evaluate the Safety and Preliminary Efficacy of Activated Recombinant Factor VII (NovoSeven®) in Acute Intracerebral Haemorrhage</official_title>
  <sponsors>
